This directory contains tools required for development, maintenance and
release management of Einarc. It's generally not interesting for regular
users, so it should be excluded from distribution tarball.

== Memo: how to make a release

1. Pump version in:
	VERSION
	src/raid/baseraid.rb
2. Document changes in NEWS
3. Commit everything
4. release-tarball
5. Upload to SF
6. Announce at:
	inquisitor.ru
	SourceForge.net (news submit)
	freshmeat.net
	linux.org.ru
	opennet.ru
